<!--
<PlayerType> tag is now necessary to activate a spawn
Valid NPC players for spawns:
	40 = BARBARIAN_PLAYER
	41 = NEANDERTHAL_PLAYER
	42 = BEAST_PLAYER
	43 = PREDATOR_PLAYER
	44 = PREY_PLAYER
	45 = INSECT_PLAYER
	46 = NPC4_PLAYER
	47 = NPC3_PLAYER
	48 = NPC2_PLAYER
	49 = NPC1_PLAYER
	50 = NPC0_PLAYER

 <iMaxLocalDensity> Range: 1-49
	Based on an area of 49 plots, 3 plots out in all directions.
	Plots that is not of the same area as the spawn plot is not counted.
	iAreaPlots (1-49) / iMaxLocalDensity (1-49) = Max units inside the Area. (Min. 1)
	Set it to 1 for a max. limit of 49 units inside the area.
	Set it to 49 for a max. limit of 1 unit inside the area.
-->
